Paper: hep-th/9810001

Date: 1998-10-01

Title: A Modified Scheme of Triplectic Quantization

Authors: B. Geyer, D.M. Gitman and P.M. Lavrov

Comments: 8 pages

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A14 (1999) 661-670

A modified version of triplectic quantization, first introduce by Batalin andMartnelius, is proposed which makes use of two independent master equations,one for the action and one for the gauge functional such that the initialclassical action also obeys that master equation.